**Summary:** This documentation covers Heatmaps functionality in Amplitude's Session Replay feature, which provides visual representations of user engagement through click maps, selector maps, and scroll maps for web-based applications, requiring Session Replay Browser SDK Plugin 1.7.0+ or Standalone SDK 1.14.0+ and available only for Growth/Enterprise plans.

